high_descs: Walk across the room, towards the black, round table, then turn right and go to the stove.
Pick up the fry pan on the front left corner of the stove.
Turn to your left and go to the back of the black, round table.
Place the fry pan in front of the apple and tomato, on the black, round table,
Pick up the apple, that is on a fork, on the black, round table.
Place the apple on the fry pan.
anns.task_desc: Put a fry pan containing an apple, on the table.

high_descs: Move forward, then turn right, go to the stove.
Pick up the front left pan on the stove.
Bring the pan to the black table on the left.
Put the pan on the table.
Pick up the apple on the table.
Put the apple in the pan on the table.
anns.task_desc: Put an apple in a pan on the table.

high_descs: Put the pan on the table.
Put the apple on the pan.
anns.task_desc: Putting a pan on the table with an apple on the pan.
